as disrespectful.

558
00:28:30,458 --> 00:28:33,127
When you're 45 minutes
late for work,

559
00:28:33,128 --> 00:28:35,629
it forces people
to have to cover for you.

560
00:28:35,630 --> 00:28:39,466
